# Deepgram API Key Setup
# Get your API key from https://console.deepgram.com/
# Deepgram offers $200 free credit to start

# For LOCAL development only (optional - key will be in browser bundle):
# VITE_DEEPGRAM_API_KEY=your_deepgram_api_key_here

# For PRODUCTION (Vercel), add DEEPGRAM_API_KEY as an environment variable
# in the Vercel dashboard. This keeps the key secure on the server.
# Go to: Vercel Dashboard > Your Project > Settings > Environment Variables
# Add: DEEPGRAM_API_KEY = your_deepgram_api_key_here
